# Daily Digest API Test Requests
# These requests test the daily digest functionality

### Get today's digest
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/digest
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get today's digest (alternative endpoint)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/digest/today
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get digest for specific date
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/digest/date/2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get weekly digests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/digest/weekly
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get digest summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/digest/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}